== 地理 ==
{{Main|新加坡地理}}
{{See also|新加坡的离岸岛屿}}
[[File:Satellite_image_of_Singapore_(Landsat_7)_-_20000428.jpg|thumb]]

新加坡共有大小岛屿63个，地势起伏和缓，主岛新加坡岛的面积占到90%以上<ref>{{cite book |first1=Victor R. |last1= Savage |first2=Brenda S.A. |last2= Yeoh |title=Toponymics: A Study of Singapore's Street Names |accessdate=2011-05-01 |year=2004 |publisher=Eastern Universities Press |location =Singapore |isbn=978-981-210-364-2}}</ref>。於北部建有[[新柔长堤|新柔长堤]]，西部有[[第二通道|第二通道]]，两者成为新加坡与马來西亚[[柔佛|柔佛]]間的通联系道。新加坡岛以外較大的有岛屿[[裕廊岛|裕廊岛]]、[[德光岛|德光岛]]、[[乌敏岛|乌敏岛]]及[[圣淘沙|圣淘沙]]，地理最高点为[[武吉知马|武吉知马]]，海拔{{convert|163.63|m|ft|0}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://heritagetrails.sg/content/148/Bukit_Timah_Hill.html |publisher=Heritage Trails |accessdate=2010-04-22 |title=Bukit Timah Hill |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100205015600/http://heritagetrails.sg/content/148/Bukit_Timah_Hill.html |archivedate=2010-02-05 }}</ref>。

新加坡很多国土都是[[填海|填海]]产生，建國後曾經進行多次填海工程。至2013年3月，填海土地面積達到逾13,000公頃，佔據新加坡原有國家土地面積達約1/4。1950年至今，約20%的国土面积由填海产生，新加坡國土面積於1960年代時為{{convert|581.5|km2|sqmi}}，現在約為{{convert|728|km2|sqmi}}，至2030年以前，將會增加{{convert|100|km2|sqmi|-1}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Towards Environmental Sustainability, State of the Environment 2005 Report |url=http://app.nea.gov.sg/counter/nea_soecover.asp |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623124946/http://www.nea.gov.sg/cms/ccird/soe/soe_cover.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-23 |publisher=Ministry of the Environment and Water Resources |accessdate=2010-04-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，部分計畫則連結比較小的島嶼，包括裕廊島<ref name="earthshots.usgs.gov">{{cite web |url= http://earthshots.usgs.gov/Singapore/Singapore |title= Earthshots: Satellite Images of Environmental Change: Singapore |publisher= Earthshots |accessdate= 2011-02-18 |archive-date= 2011-05-10 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110510074806/http://earthshots.usgs.gov/Singapore/Singapore |dead-url= no }}</ref>。尽管都市化缩减了[[雨林|雨林]]面積，新加坡約有23%的國土屬於森林或自然保護區<ref>{{cite web |url=http://earthtrends.wri.org/pdf_library/country_profiles/for_cou_702.pdf |title=Forests, grasslands and drylands – Singapore |publisher=World Resources Institute |year=2003 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2005-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050601091338/http://earthtrends.wri.org/pdf_library/country_profiles/for_cou_702.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，森林主要分布於[[武吉知马自然保护区|武吉知马自然保护区]]<ref name="earthshots.usgs.gov"/>。新加坡在城市綠化方面相當成功，境內共有逾300座公園及4個自然保護區，有「花園城市」之稱<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nparks.gov.sg/cms/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=198&Itemid=66#_ftnref2 |title=Interesting facts of our Garden City |publisher=National Parks Board |accessdate=2011-10-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123103354/http://www.nparks.gov.sg/cms/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=198&Itemid=66#_ftnref2 |archivedate=2012-01-23 }}</ref>。

新加坡並無採行[[夏時制|夏時制]]，[[新加坡標準時間|新加坡標準時間]]為[[UTC+8|UTC+8]]，較其地理位置時間快1小時<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.math.nus.edu.sg/aslaksen/teaching/timezone.html |title=Why is Singapore in the "Wrong" Time Zone? |author=Mok Ly Yng |publisher=National University of Singapore |date=2010-09-22 |accessdate=2011-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100728230528/http://www.math.nus.edu.sg/aslaksen/teaching/timezone.html |archive-date=2010-07-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

新加坡地处[[热带|热带]]，长年受[[赤道低压带|赤道低压带]]控制，为[[赤道多雨气候|赤道多雨气候]]，长夏无冬，气温年温差和日温差小，年平均温度在24摄氏度至34摄氏度之间：最冷月为1月，受来自中国的东北[[季风|季风]]影响，加上低压带的南移，较干燥的东北风会令新加坡的平均低温徘徊在摄氏23至24度左右。在此期间，新加坡的天气也会比较好；而到了4月至5月这段期间， 在低压带的北移和东亚大陆高压带的减弱的影响下，气温会有轻微回升，而且雨量也会增多，湿度较高，每日平均相对湿度早上为79%，下午為73%<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/weather/forecast/89?state=fo:D#fo:D |title=Weather – Singapore |work=BBC News |accessdate=2011-04-13 |archive-date=2011-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110921074405/http://news.bbc.co.uk/weather/forecast/89?state=fo:D#fo:D |dead-url=no }}</ref>。降雨充足，也常有[[雷暴|雷暴]]，年均降雨量在2,400毫米左右，每年11月到1月为雨季，受較潮濕的季風影響，雨水较多<ref>{{cite web |url=http://app2.nea.gov.sg/weather_statistics.aspx |title=Weather Statistics |publisher=[[國家環境局|國家環境局]] |accessdate=2010-04-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100428141045/http://app2.nea.gov.sg/weather_statistics.aspx |archivedate=2010-04-28 }}</ref>。而每年的6月至9月，吹西南季候風，較為乾燥少雨。

