== 文化 ==
=== 人口 ===
{{Main|新加坡人口}}

[[File:Singapore_Merlion-at-Marina-Bay-03.jpg|thumb]]]]
[[File:EsplanadeAerial.JPG|thumb]]狀的[[濱海藝術中心|濱海藝術中心]]，矗立在濱海廣場的前面，空照圖]]

新加坡是世界[[人口密度|人口密度]]第三高的國家或地区，次於[[摩納哥|摩納哥]]和[[澳門|澳門]]。

到2018年中为止，新加坡常住人口为563.87万人，其中347.2万人（61.6%）属于本国公民，其他則屬永久居民或外籍勞工，有23%本國公民在新加坡以外地區出生，永久居民約有50萬人<ref name="unpop" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.singstat.gov.sg/pubn/popn/c2010acr.pdf |title=Census of population |publisher=Singapore Department of Statistics |year=2010 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68v15isAU?url=http://www.singstat.gov.sg/pubn/popn/c2010acr.pdf |archivedate=2012-07-05 }}</ref><ref name="singstat"/>。

新加坡人口年齡中位數為37歲，每戶平均人口為3.5人，由於土地不足，約五分之四的新加坡人居住於一般稱為[[组屋|组屋]]的[[公共房屋|公共房屋]]（政府部份資助購買的廉價質房屋）<ref name="hdb">{{cite web |url=http://www.hdb.gov.sg/fi10/fi10320p.nsf/w/HDBWinsUNAward?OpenDocument |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-10-14  |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111211145036/http://www.hdb.gov.sg/fi10/fi10320p.nsf/w/HDBWinsUNAward?OpenDocument |archivedate=2011-12-11 }}</ref>。至2010年，已有四分之三的人口居住於4房或以上的組屋或私有住宅，住宅自給率則達87.2%<ref name="Singapore Department of Statistics">{{cite web |url=http://www.singstat.gov.sg/stats/themes/people/popnindicators.pdf |title=Key demographic indicators, 1970–2010 |publisher=Singapore Department of Statistics |year=2010 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316082834/http://www.singstat.gov.sg/stats/themes/people/popnindicators.pdf |archivedate=2012-03-16 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.singstat.gov.sg/pubn/popn/c2010acr/tA6.pdf |title=Resident Population by Place of Birth, Ethnic Group and Sex |publisher=Singapore Department of Statistics |year=2010 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110607034144/http://www.singstat.gov.sg/pubn/popn/c2010acr/tA6.pdf |archivedate=2011-06-07 }}</ref>。[[行動電話|行動電話]]普及率則高達每千人擁有1,400支行動電話，約十分之一的居民擁有汽車<ref name="singstat" />。

新加坡[[总和生育率|总和生育率]]一直處于低水平，於2012年估計每個婦女平均的生育子女數為0.78名嬰兒，小於人口置換的2.1<ref name=CIA/>；為了解決此項問題，[[新加坡政府|新加坡政府]]在過去數十年鼓勵外國人民移居新加坡，而大量移民也使新加坡人口並未減少<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/257208/1/.html |title=Singapore's birth trend outlook remains dismal |work=Channel NewsAsia |location=Singapore |date=2007-02-07 |first=Julia |last=Ng |accessdate=2010-04-22 |archive-date=2010-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113223503/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/257208/1/.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

新加坡為世界上[[各国失业率列表|失業率最低的國家]]之一，過去十年間失業率未曾超過4%，失業率於[[2000年代後期環球金融危機|2009年全球金融危機]]達到高峰，失業率為3%，至2011年降回1.9%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mom.gov.sg/statistics-publications/national-labour-market-information/statistics/Pages/unemployment.aspx |title=Unemployment |publisher=Ministry of Manpower |year=2010 |accessdate=2011-07-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110626055537/http://www.mom.gov.sg/statistics-publications/national-labour-market-information/statistics/Pages/unemployment.aspx |archivedate=2011-06-26 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/1135224/1/.html |title=S'pore unemployment rate falls to three-year low |publisher=Channel NewsAsia |date=2011-06-15 |author=Chan, Joanne |accessdate=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2013-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130117011942/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/1135224/1/.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

於2009年時，約四成的居民為外國移民，為[[各国移民数列表|比率最高的國家]]之一<ref name="un.org">[http://www.un.org/esa/population/publications/migration/UN_MigStock_2008.pdf "Trends in international migrant stock: The 2008 revision"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.un.org/esa/population/publications/migration/UN_MigStock_2008.pdf |date=20171020155111 }}, United Nations, Department of Economic and Social Affairs, Population Division (2009).</ref>，雖然外國移民對於國家經濟相當重要，但政府考慮限制外國勞動力，外國勞動力組成了80%的建造業及50%的服務業勞動力<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.asiaone.com/Business/News/Office/Story/A1Story20090222-123635.html |title=Singapore's phantom workers |last=Sudderuddin |first=Shuli |newspaper=The Straits Times |location=Singapore |date=2009-02-22 |accessdate=2011-04-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225121552/http://www.asiaone.com/Business/News/Office/Story/A1Story20090222-123635.html |archivedate=2009-02-25 }}</ref>。

2009年，在本地居民（本国公民及永久居民的總稱）中，[[新加坡华人|華人]]占74.2%，而[[欧亚混血|欧亚混血]]人口和其他族群（包括[[峇峇娘惹|峇峇娘惹]]）则占3.2%，[[马来人|马来人]]占13.4%，[[新加坡印度人|印度裔]]（以[[泰米尔人|泰米尔人]]居多）占9.2%。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/1030142/1/.html |title=Singaporeans of mixed race allowed to 'double barrel' race in IC |work=Channel NewsAsia |location=Singapore |author=Hoe Yeen Nie |date=2010-01-12 |accessdate=2011-02-18 |archive-date=2010-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100206100917/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/stories/singaporelocalnews/view/1030142/1/.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[新加坡华人|新加坡华人]]的祖先大部分源自[[中華人民共和國|中国]][[福建省|福建]]、[[广东省|广东]]和[[海南省|海南]]等地。<ref>{{cite web|date=2017-06-01|script-title=zh:簡說新加坡華人族群|url=https://vitomag.com/history/asbkti.html|work=移民人物誌|access-date=2020-04-22|language=zh|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322215026/https://vitomag.com/history/asbkti.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

